values.name: gazebo
values.description: fork to prepare IR-Lock simulation and plugin to gazebo

values.name: gazebo8-win32
values.description:
Aiming for a windows build of gazebo8

Fork objectives:
1. All dependencies to be obtained via NuGet or vcpkg or Conan or Chocolatey.
2. Minimise binaries stored in repo.
3. Minimise divergence of fork from main gazebo repo.
4. Build supported using VS 2017
5. Release a downloadable win32 build
6. Test/fix on Windows 10 (x64 desktop) platform
7. PR if all goes well to reintegrate with origin
